data.description: Country home with lots of updates! This recently refinished home boasts one floor living with 3 bedrooms and 1 bathroom. Enjoy the newer paint, carpet, and newer laminate flooring throughout.  Enjoy a nice front porch and back decks. Plenty of storage space with a 24x28 garage and additional shed. Located on approximately half an acre.  Located in Grand Junction and only a short drive to Bangor and South Haven.
